{"tid":2076136,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港台英語節目播歌有粗俗用語　遭通訊局警告","createTime":"2020-06-23T09:54:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T09:57:10.000Z","uid":60281,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ef784462e00ac7ecee80e24b4741bf5470eabac4","tid":2076136,"uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T09:54:47.000Z","msg":"乜歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n通訊局裁定兩宗涉及香港電台節目的投訴成立，其中一宗向港台發出警告。<br />\n<br />\n裁決指出，一名公眾人士投訴港台英語頻道第三台電台節目《Simon Willson》，於去年12月15日播放的一首歌曲《Jackie Chan》數次出現粗俗用語。<br />\n<br />\n通訊局考慮了包括港台陳述的資料，認為用語在歌曲多次出現，可清楚聽到，該等用語明顯惹人反感，不可接受在有關節目中播出，明顯違反《電台節目守則》規定，裁定投訴成立。考慮到個案是港台的電台節目服務不足兩年內第三度違反規管用語的條文，決定向港台發出警告，並敦促港台嚴格遵守《守則》條文。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1533658-20200623.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1533658-20200623.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=91nyg34XrGq4aGOua7i4JamkGRIJ7ARjMQoHd6uTSg0%3D&h=6672f89c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1533658-20200623.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=5e4898dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1533658-20200623.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"4fdf4aeab30042acf94d90f39353c92c280b1e0c","tid":2076136,"uid":55493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T09:56:34.000Z","msg":"Jackie chan"},{"pid":"a9d7ff01d8943e096a05c30df19aec874ac0841c","tid":2076136,"uid":117837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T09:56:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6DaL-Z4dwzI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6DaL-Z4dwzI&d=91nyg34XrGq4aGOua7i4JamkGRIJ7ARjMQoHd6uTSg0%3D&